Reasoning: The paper deals with the performance of MIMO wireless systems with imperfect channel knowledge, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT), communication systems (cs.COMM), and system and control theory (cs.SY). The use of space modulation techniques also falls under the category of multiple access communication (cs.NI).
